home.company-address: Address: 7th Floor, Hoang Ngoc Building, No. 4 Lane 82, Dich Vong Hau Street, Cau Giay, Hanoi
home.future-content-1: Customers can create a convenient support request quickly so that the building management can fix problems in time, helping customers always have the best experience.
home.future-content: Customers evaluate and give suggestions about the service quality of the building. Help management to fix and improve service quality to bring the best experience to customers
home.intro-content: Allows asset management, operation management department to have an overall, intuitive and immediate view of the operation status of all office buildings being managed by MB-AMC. With the management boards of each building, they will digitize the operation process of the building they manage. At the same time, scheduling maintenance, repair, approval to purchase replacement equipment will become clear and easy to manage.
